WEBVTT

14:42.060 --> 14:43.640 line:80%
According to the Legal Code of Great Yin，

14:43.640 --> 14:44.730 line:80%
if a household has no male heir,

14:44.730 --> 14:45.950 line:80%
the house goes to the next of kin.

14:45.950 --> 14:47.160 line:80%
If the older brother dies,
the younger succeeds.

14:47.160 --> 14:48.830 line:80%
-And if the younger brother dies...
-That's nonsense!

14:48.830 --> 14:50.280 line:80%
That's nonsense.
